descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#6aa84f][b][u][size=5]It's Finally Here! Immersive Riften Breads![/size][/u][/b][/color][/center]
[size=4]Sorry about all the confusion, here's a video to suit your needs, and a map.
No conflicts ;~;
[/size][youtube]Fwy1g7xZFPs[/youtube]

[size=4]Ever wondered why there's no bread at the gate in Riften? How un-lore friendly it is? Yeah? Me too, but worry no longer! This mod adds a piece of Bread to the gate in Riften! Not just any bread though, godly bread. The only one in the game, of course. Now you can eat that right up and gain 2 health, man, good stuff.[/size]
